    "created_at": "2014-04-26T20:29:16Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-04-26T20:29:16Z",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I tried with the following template (mytemplate.tplx), which works fine for me:\n\n```\n((*- extends 'report.tplx' -*))\n\n((* block h1 -*))\\chapter((* endblock h1 -*))\n((* block h2 -*))\\section((* endblock h2 -*))\n((* block h3 -*))\\subsection((* endblock h3 -*))\n((* block h4 -*))\\subsubsection((* endblock h4 -*))\n((* block h5 -*))\\paragraph((* endblock h5 -*))\n((* block h6 -*))\\subparagraph((* endblock h6 -*))\n```\n\nrunning with\n`ipython nbconvert --to latex --template mytemplate.tplx notebook.ipynb`\n"
  },
